1:38:01.000 --> 1:38:02.541
I have loved no one but you."

1:38:04.416 --> 1:38:06.041
"And I don't think I ever will."

1:38:24.166 --> 1:38:25.250
Anne.

1:38:27.041 --> 1:38:30.333
