-I wish you both every happiness.

1:38:40.083 --> 1:38:42.416
"I have thought many times
about how to tell you,

1:38:43.000 --> 1:38:45.916
but the pain of a love unrequited
rendered me silent."

1:38:47.291 --> 1:38:49.250
"Tell me not that I am too late."

1:38:50.333 --> 1:38:51.166
Frederick!

1:38:52.750 --> 1:38:55.583
"My love for you
has never faltered."

